  ('proverbs-wisdom-5', 'proverbs-wisdom', 'THERE IS A WAY WHICH SEEMETH RIGHT', 'Warning that ends in death.', 'Proverbs 14:12 — There is a way which seemeth right unto a man, but the end t', 'Proverbs 14:12', 'There is a way which seemeth right unto a man, but the end thereof are the ways of death. 13 Even in laughter the heart is sorrowful; and the end of that mirth is heaviness. 14 The backslider in heart shall be filled with his own ways: and a', 'Seeming right is not the same as being right.', 4)
